--config-dir=.`, ensuring that `~~/` path expansion correctly identifies the project's `script-opts` directory even when running with `--no-config`. All 15 test scenarios passed successfully in the headless test environment. | Test File | Status | Scenarios | |:--|:--|:--| | `test_reg_20260508_anki.py` | ✅ PASSED | 3 | | `test_reg_20260508_config.py` | ✅ PASSED | 4 | | `test_reg_20260508_core.py` | ✅ PASSED | 8 | The new tests are located in `tests/acceptance/` and can be run using: ```powershell python -m pytest tests/acceptance/test_reg_20260508_*.py ```
